## NOTE FOR FRONTEND DEVELOPER

### Authentication

```javascript
// Sign up
await supabase.auth.signUp({ email, password })

// Sign in
await supabase.auth.signInWithPassword({ email, password })

// Google sign in
await supabase.auth.signInWithOAuth({ provider: 'google' })

// Sign out
await supabase.auth.signOut()

// Get current user
const { data: { user } } = await supabase.auth.getUser()
```

### Student APIs

```javascript
// Get dashboard stats
const { data } = await supabase
  .rpc('get_student_dashboard_stats', { user_uuid: user.id })

// Get my courses with progress
const { data } = await supabase
  .rpc('get_my_courses', { user_uuid: user.id })

// Get recent activity
const { data } = await supabase
  .rpc('get_recent_activity', { 
    user_uuid: user.id, 
    limit_count: 10 
  })

// Mark lesson complete
await supabase
  .from('progress')
  .insert({ user_id: user.id, lesson_id: 5, completed: true })

// Get notifications
const { data } = await supabase
  .rpc('get_my_notifications', { p_limit: 20 })

// Mark notification read
await supabase
  .rpc('mark_notification_read', { p_notification_id: 123 })

// Delete my account
await supabase.rpc('delete_my_account')
```

### Admin APIs

```javascript
// Check if current user is admin
const { data: isAdmin } = await supabase.rpc('is_admin')

// Get all users (admin only)
const { data } = await supabase
  .from('users')
  .select('*')
  .order('created_at', { ascending: false })

// Ban user
await supabase.rpc('ban_user', { 
  target_user_id: 'uuid-here', 
  reason: 'spam' 
})

// Unban user
await supabase.rpc('unban_user', { target_user_id: 'uuid-here' })

// Create course
await supabase
  .from('courses')
  .insert({ title, description, instructor })

// Update course
await supabase
  .from('courses')
  .update({ title })
  .eq('id', courseId)

// Delete course
await supabase
  .from('courses')
  .delete()
  .eq('id', courseId)

// Add module
await supabase
  .from('modules')
  .insert({ course_id, title, order })

// Add lesson
await supabase
  .from('lessons')
  .insert({ module_id, title, youtube_video_id, order })

// Add quiz
await supabase
  .from('quizzes')
  .insert({ lesson_id, question, options, correct_answer })
```

### Public APIs (no login needed)

```javascript
// Get all courses
const { data } = await supabase
  .from('courses')
  .select('*, modules:modules(*, lessons:lessons(*))')

// Get single course
const { data } = await supabase
  .from('courses')
  .select('*, modules:modules(*, lessons:lessons(*))')
  .eq('id', courseId)
  .single()
```

### YouTube Integration

```javascript
// Embed YouTube video
<iframe
  src={`https://www.youtube.com/embed/${youtubeVideoId}?rel=0&modestbranding=1`}
  title={lessonTitle}
  frameBorder="0"
  allowFullScreen
/>

// Extract video ID from URL
function getYouTubeId(url) {
  const regExp = /^.*(youtu.be\/|v\/|u\/\w\/|embed\/|watch\?v=|&v=)([^#&?]*).*/
  const match = url.match(regExp)
  return match && match[2].length === 11 ? match[2] : null
}
```

### Tables Reference

| Table | Used for |
|-------|----------|
| users | Profiles, roles |
| courses | Course catalog |
| modules | Course sections |
| lessons | Individual videos |
| enrollments | Which user enrolled which course |
| progress | Completed lessons |
| quizzes | Questions and answers |
| quiz_attempts | User quiz submissions |
| certificates | Earned certificates |
| notifications | User alerts |

### Important Rules

1. **Never trust client-side role checks** - RLS enforces on database
2. **Always check `is_admin()`** before showing admin UI
3. **Banned users** - Check `is_banned` on every page load
4. **Progress auto-saves** when lesson marked complete
5. **Certificate auto-generates** when course 100% complete
6. **YouTube videos** - Use `?rel=0&modestbranding=1` parameters

